{
  "texts": [
    "Discussions",
    "The emergence of transformer technology is due to the interaction and convergence of competencies from mathematics and model design in neural networks.",
    "Transformer architecture was introduced in the context of natural language processing (NLP), but they have shown to be versatile and powerful, finding new applications in diverse fields such as computer vision, speech recognition, etc.",
    "In the realm of neural networks, the Transformer architecture has emerged as a transformative force, initially revolutionizing natural language processing and subsequently finding applications in diverse domains.",
    "Before transformers, recurrent neural networks (RNNs) had many limitations, but a main breakthrough is the introduction of the self-attention mechanism, which intuitively mimics cognitive attention."
  ]
}